                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><persName>Is. Valencia</persName> &amp; family, <persName>M. H.\n                                                  Baiz</persName> &amp; family; <persName>Is. Jes.\n                                                  Lindo</persName> &amp; family; <persName>A.\n                                                  H.<lb/> Moron</persName> &amp; family;\n                                                  <persName>Michl. Perrso</persName> &amp; lady;\n                                                  <persName>Abm. Jes Lindo</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Danl Delima</persName>.<lb/> (to be\n                                        married to <persName>Miss Sar. Valencia</persName>)\n                                                  <persName>Josiah L. Henriguez</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Mordy R. Caprilles</persName><lb/> &amp;\n                                        myself beside a son of <persName>Mr. M H Baiz</persName> who\n                                        is already over 13 years.,—you<lb/> will therefore observe\n                                        that we complete full Minyan, even<lb/> for\n                                                  <date>Kipur</date>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Should you deem these Items worthy of occupying a\n                                        space<lb/> in your valuable journal, I will feel most proud\n                                        of having added to<lb/> your gen<hi rend=\"sup\">l</hi>.\n                                        Stock.   Meanwhile I subscribe myself</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Revd. Sir! Your most Ob<hi rend=\"sup\">t</hi>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Sam Piza</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
